{"parse":{"title":"Marcy Blum","pageid":14819280,"revid":842354186,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Marcy Blum</b> is an American author, event planner and owner of Marcy Blum Associates in <a href=\"/wiki/New_York_City\" title=\"New York City\">New York City</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Education\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Education</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Career\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Career</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Personal\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Personal</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Education\">Education</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Marcy_Blum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Education\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Blum is a graduate of <a href=\"/wiki/The_Culinary_Institute_of_America\" title=\"The Culinary Institute of America\">The Culinary Institute of America</a> and began her career in the restaurant business, later creating a segue into the then developing field of <a href=\"/wiki/Event_planning\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Event planning\">event planning</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-nys1_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-nys1-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> In 1986<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> she became one of the first in the industry to develop the vocation into a successful career<sup id=\"cite_ref-nys1_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-nys1-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Career\">Career</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Marcy_Blum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Career\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Blum has been a guest on the <i><a href=\"/wiki/CBS_Morning_Show\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"CBS Morning Show\">CBS Morning Show</a></i>, <i><a href=\"/wiki/Today_(NBC_program)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Today (NBC program)\">The Today Show</a></i>, <i><a href=\"/wiki/Live_with_Regis_and_Kelly\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Live with Regis and Kelly\">Live with Regis and Kelly</a></i>, <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Oprah_Winfrey_Show\" title=\"The Oprah Winfrey Show\">The Oprah Winfrey Show</a></i> and <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Nate_Berkus_Show\" title=\"The Nate Berkus Show\">The Nate Berkus Show</a>.</i><sup class=\"noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">&#91;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed\" title=\"Wikipedia:Citation needed\"><span title=\"This claim needs references to reliable sources. (January 2014)\">citation needed</span></a></i>&#93;</sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Among her clients are <a href=\"/wiki/Billy_Joel\" title=\"Billy Joel\">Billy Joel</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Katie_Lee_Joel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Katie Lee Joel\">Katie Lee Joel</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/wiki/Kevin_Bacon\" title=\"Kevin Bacon\">Kevin Bacon</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Kyra_Sedgwick\" title=\"Kyra Sedgwick\">Kyra Sedgwick</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Salman_Rushdie\" title=\"Salman Rushdie\">Salman Rushdie</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Padma_Lakshmi\" title=\"Padma Lakshmi\">Padma Lakshmi</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Colin_Hanks\" title=\"Colin Hanks\">Colin Hanks</a> and Samantha Bryant, <a href=\"/wiki/LeBron_James\" title=\"LeBron James\">Lebron James</a> and Savannah James,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Williams_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Williams-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/wiki/George_Soros\" title=\"George Soros\">George Soros</a> and Tomiko Soros,<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/wiki/Rockefeller_family\" title=\"Rockefeller family\">Rockefeller family</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Nate_Berkus\" title=\"Nate Berkus\">Nate Berkus</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Jeremiah_Brent\" title=\"Jeremiah Brent\">Jeremiah Brent</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/wiki/Andre_Iguodala\" title=\"Andre Iguodala\">Andre Iguodala</a> and Christina Iguodala.<sup id=\"cite_ref-nys1_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-nys1-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> She was also the planner of <a href=\"/wiki/The_Knot_Inc.\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Knot Inc.\">The Knot</a>'s \"Dream Wedding\" in 2014 of Boston Marathon bombing survivors, Rebekah Gregory and Pete DiMartino.<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> <i><a href=\"/wiki/New_York_magazine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"New York magazine\">New York</a></i> magazine described Blum as a \"desired wedding planner to the wealthy and famous.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><i><a href=\"/wiki/Vogue_(magazine)\" title=\"Vogue (magazine)\">Vogue Magazine</a></i> named Blum one of the top wedding planners in the world by,<sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup> <i><a href=\"/wiki/Harper%27s_Bazaar\" title=\"Harper&#39;s Bazaar\">Harper's Bazaar</a></i>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/wiki/Martha_Stewart_Living_Omnimedia\" title=\"Martha Stewart Living Omnimedia\">Martha Stewart Weddings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-14\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Blum has written and contributed to many articles, including <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_New_York_Times\" title=\"The New York Times\">The New York Times</a></i>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Williams_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Williams-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <i><a href=\"/wiki/New_York_(magazine)\" title=\"New York (magazine)\">New York</a></i> magazine,<sup id=\"cite_ref-15\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup> The Knot,<sup id=\"cite_ref-16\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup> <i><a href=\"/wiki/Brides_(magazine)\" title=\"Brides (magazine)\">Brides</a></i> magazine, <i><a href=\"/wiki/Elle_(magazine)\" title=\"Elle (magazine)\">Elle</a></i>, <i>Modern Bride</i>, <i><a href=\"/wiki/InStyle\" title=\"InStyle\">InStyle</a></i>, and <i><a href=\"/wiki/Town_%26_Country_(magazine)\" title=\"Town &amp; Country (magazine)\">Town &amp; Country</a></i>.\n</p><p>She coauthored, with Laura Kaiser, two books, <i>Wedding Planning for Dummies</i> and <i>Wedding Kit for Dummies</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-nys1_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-nys1-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Personal\">Personal</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Marcy_Blum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Personal\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Marcy is the sister of American author and journalist <a href=\"/wiki/Howard_Blum\" title=\"Howard Blum\">Howard Blum</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Marcy_Blum&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist columns references-column-width\" style=\"-moz-column-width: 30em; -webkit-column-width: 30em; column-width: 30em; list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-nys1-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-nys1_1-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-nys1_1-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-nys1_1-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-nys1_1-3\"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Swerdloff, Alexis <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nysun.com/article/7482?page_no=1\">What Do Padma Lakshmi and Kyra Sedgwick Have in Common? Their Wedding Planner,</a> <a href=\"/wiki/New_York_Sun\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"New York Sun\">New York Sun</a></i>, January 11, 2005</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Mallozzi, Vincent M.; Gettleman, Jeffrey <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/24/fashion/24planner.html?pagewanted=1&amp;ref=fashion\">Taming the Runaway Wedding Planner,</a> <a href=\"/wiki/The_New_York_Times\" title=\"The New York Times\">The New York Times</a></i>, June 24, 2007</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://weddingmarketnews.com/marcy_blum/\">\"Interview with Wedding Planner Marcy Blum  \u2013 Wedding Market\"</a>. <i>weddingmarketnews.com</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-03-19</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=weddingmarketnews.com&amp;rft.atitle=Interview+with+Wedding+Planner+Marcy+Blum++%E2%80%93+Wedding+Market&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweddingmarketnews.com%2Fmarcy_blum%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMarcy+Blum\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6874808/jimmy-iovine-liberty-ross-wedding-gift-picks\">\"Jimmy Iovine &amp; Liberty Ross Wedding Gift Picks - Billboard\"</a>. <i>Billboard</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Billboard&amp;rft.atitle=Jimmy+Iovine+%26+Liberty+Ross+Wedding+Gift+Picks+-+Billboard&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.billboard.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F6874808%2Fjimmy-iovine-liberty-ross-wedding-gift-picks&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMarcy+Blum\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Williams-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Williams_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Williams_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Williams, Alex (2015-08-15). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/15/fashion/jennifer-aniston-justin-theroux-how-celebrities-keep-their-weddings-a-secret.html\">\"How Celebrities Keep Their Weddings a Secret\"</a>. <i>The New York Times</i>. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number\" title=\"International Standard Serial Number\">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/issn/0362-4331\">0362-4331</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-03-19</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft.atitle=How+Celebrities+Keep+Their+Weddings+a+Secret&amp;rft.date=2015-08-15&amp;rft.issn=0362-4331&amp;rft.aulast=Williams&amp;rft.aufirst=Alex&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2015%2F08%2F15%2Ffashion%2Fjennifer-aniston-justin-theroux-how-celebrities-keep-their-weddings-a-secret.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMarcy+Blum\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-soros-wedding-idUSBRE98J0XZ20130922\">\"Billionaire Soros weds consultant in third marriage\"</a>. <i>Reuters</i>. 2013-09-22<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-03-19</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Reuters&amp;rft.atitle=Billionaire+Soros+weds+consultant+in+third+marriage&amp;rft.date=2013-0